"78:25:3" : {s: 78, a: 25, w: 3, r: "غسق", t: "وَغَسَّاقًۭا", l: "غَسَّاق", lc: 2, tl: "waghassāqan", lb: "দুর্গন্ধময় (পানি)",e: "and purulence", b: "রক্ত-পূঁজ", i: "dan air luka dan nanah", f: 1, rm: "darkness, the night; become obscure, shed tears, poured water; ice-cold darkness, intense coldness; watery/thick purulent matter that flows or drips, dark/murky/cold fluid."},
"78:26:1" : {s: 78, a: 26, w: 1, r: "جزي", t: "جَزَآءًۭ", l: "جَزَآء", lc: 42, tl: "jazāan", lb: "প্রতিদান, বিনিময়, পুরস্কার, বদলা",e: "A recompense", b: "শাস্তিস্বরূপ", i: "pembalasan", f: 15, rm: "Pay/give/render a satisfaction, make sufficient, pay a debt, to contend, repay/requit/compensate, to recompense."},
