"78:27:4" : {s: 78, a: 27, w: 4, r: "رجو", t: "يَرْجُونَ", l: "يَرْجُوا۟", lc: 22, tl: "yarjūna", lb: "কামনা করা",e: "expecting", b: "তারা আশা করে", i: "mengharapkan", f: 11, rm: "to hope/expect, an opinion requiring the happening of an event in which will be a cause of happiness; expectation of deriving advantage from an event of which a cause has already occurred, keep awaited, put off, put aside, defer/delay, fear, beg/request. arja (pl.) - borders, sides. marjowwon is a person in whom great hopes are placed (e.g. 11:62)."},
